com.dooapp.gaedo.properties
Interface Property

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractPropertyAdapter, ClassCollectionProperty, DelegateProperty, DescribedProperty, PropertyField, TypeProperty
public interface Property

A property is our vision of what a bean attribute is. Notice implementors of this interface must implement equals and hashcode for semantic equality
